title: Dana Perino: Republicans Do Not Want To Outlaw Abortions
text:
John Gibson Aug 4, 2015 
The Five’s Dana Perino spoke with Gibson about the latest on Planned Parenthood allegedly selling aborted fetus’s body parts. 
Listen here: Listen to audio clip. 
Dana told Gibson she is really surprised Elisabeth Warren and Hillary Clinton would say that republicans are trying to take away abortion rights when that is clearly not the case. Dana said if you strip away your humanity, then you can understand where the left is coming from in their defense of Planned Parenthood.
